snippet.title: Get a Grip Chip and the Body Bugs Trailer
snippet.description:
Send tiny robotic hero Chip on a new mission inside the human body to dismantle digestive distress! In this satisfying 2D platformer, master Chip’s grappling hook and get things flowing through the digestive system. Raise an army of white blood cells to fight off the Body Bugs as you grapple for guts and glory.
#IDatXbox #IDXbox #ID_Xbox
